script = ExtResource("3_15ils")
barrel_id = 45
barrel_name = "Kinematic Equation"
barrel_desc = "[b]Kinematic Equation Barrel[/b]
Speed equal distance divided by time. Or so I remembered. Nothing to do with card game at all.

Possible rolls:
[ul]
Slow Roller: Your bullets are slower, but they have increased damage the longer they travelled.
Long Shot: Your bullets are more accurate, and deal more damage the further its target.
Snap Call: Your bullets are faster, and deal more damage the higher their speed. Minimal benefit for hitscan weapon though.
[/ul]
"
